edu.cmu.sphinx.frontend.feature

Class FeatureTransform

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cmu.sphinx.util.props.ConfigurableAdapter
      • edu.cmu.sphinx.frontend.BaseDataProcessor
        • edu.cmu.sphinx.frontend.feature.FeatureTransform
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataProcessor, Configurable

    public class FeatureTransform
extends BaseDataProcessor
    Implements a linear feature transformation transformation. It might be a dimension reduction or just a decorrelation transform. This component requires a special model trained with LDA/MLLT transform.
